The paper focuses on quality assurance in IoT systems, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and security (cs.CR) aspects. The study also involves analyzing and categorizing research papers, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, IoT systems involve networking and communication (cs.NI) and control systems (cs.SY) aspects, which are also relevant to the study.
